{"tid":1948768,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3000警員出現症狀","createTime":"2020-03-29T08:22:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T09:03:04.000Z","uid":213167,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"81b3f78982609c222df474ba87cd9218d37c20ff","tid":1948768,"uid":213167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T08:22:06.000Z","msg":"NYPD逾500人確診 3000警員出現症狀<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.singtaousa.com/wp-content/uploads/master/2020/03/NYB16P03280320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.singtaousa.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fmaster%2F2020%2F03%2FNYB16P03280320.jpg&h=f0a112a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紐約市警本周的確診人數急增。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n紐約市警務處有超過500人對新冠病毒檢測呈陽性，並據悉有超過3000名警察出現類似流感症狀，令人擔心警員確診數字可能直線急升。此外，當局已出現第2宗死亡病例。<br />\n<br />\n綜合英國《每日郵報》、NY1及CNN報道，根據報告指出，部門有512人確診，包括442名制服警員及70名文職人員。與此同時，有4111名警員請病假，佔警隊的11%以上。<br />\n<br />\n紐約市警務處於27日日宣布，來自布朗士第49分局的文職人員巴布朗於26日晚上在家病逝，是繼62歲的總部清潔工迪克森後的第2宗死亡病例。<br />\n有消息人士透露，紐約市警務處情報和反恐部門負責人米勒也對病毒呈陽性，目前正在醫院接受治療，是第3位確診的警隊高層。<br />\n<br />\n令人擔憂的是，有3016人報告出現流感症狀，當中包括發燒、咳嗽、流鼻涕、頭痛和疲勞等與新冠病毒相同的症狀。一名警方消息人士說，「這肯定不是一個好兆頭，他們之中可能有人感染，但目前很難證實。部門希望警員如果出現任何症狀，留在家中並自行隔離，以免感染他人。」<br />\n<br />\n自周一（23日）以來，紐約市警務處的確診及請病假數字急升，當時只有129人確診及2407人請假。<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，紐約市消防局有至少206名成員對病毒測試呈陽性，比之前多75人，當中包括消防員、緊急醫療服務人員和文職人員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.singtaousa.com/home/436-%E7%B4%90%E7%B4%84/2769258-NYPD%E9%80%BE500%E4%BA%BA%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA++3000%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E7%97%87%E7%8B%80/?fbclid=IwAR39Ge_eHqhVkD1PRpnVzLtsNd9ILi4hUNMAwo6Ba0NhiV_qhfAGtB9d9LQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtaousa.com%2Fhome%2F436-%25E7%25B4%2590%25E7%25B4%2584%2F2769258-NYPD%25E9%2580%25BE500%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%2B%2B3000%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%258F%25BE%25E7%2597%2587%25E7%258B%2580%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR39Ge_eHqhVkD1PRpnVzLtsNd9ILi4hUNMAwo6Ba0NhiV_qhfAGtB9d9LQ&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe%2BF5TOcUp1XGW39uuIwQJ%2Fg%3D&h=2869f514\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.singtaousa.com/home/436-%E7%B4%90%E7%B4%84/2769258-NYPD%E9%80%BE500%E4%BA%BA%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA++3000%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E7%97%87%E7%8B%80/?fbclid=IwAR39Ge_eHqhVkD1PRpnVzLtsNd9ILi4hUNMAwo6Ba0NhiV_qhfAGtB9d9LQ</a>"},{"pid":"66e54b3c48433e3aca0e21cacfe750e1e51b5772","tid":1948768,"uid":147785,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T08:23:11.000Z","msg":"屌 興奮左一秒"},{"pid":"350475453803e72c043fa220ba36f0bc3447ed2a","tid":1948768,"uid":207917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T08:25:57.000Z","msg":"屌，以為你講香港"},{"pid":"53f6d9ff7d43a5a1e56826b01cf668ffb1b348db","tid":1948768,"uid":310970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T08:27:19.000Z","msg":"屌，加美國係標題係唔係好難？"},{"pid":"a74535b8c15a6523dd9f8556f95e08df8ffac7a1","tid":1948768,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"350475453803e72c043fa220ba36f0bc3447ed2a","tid":1948768,"uid":207917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T08:25:57.000Z","msg":"屌，以為你講香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T08:31:50.000Z","msg":"咪撚搞笑拉港豬"},{"pid":"5837f2487c65e94dc55663a86097568a66cedbeb","tid":1948768,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T09:03:04.000Z","msg":"快啲出兵核平支那"}]}